### Common Input/Output Components

| Component | Use |
|---|---|
| `gr.Textbox()` | Text input or output. `lines=` controls height, `placeholder=` adds hint text. |
| `gr.Number()` | Numeric input or output. |
| `gr.Slider()` | Numeric range selector. Set `step=1` for integers. |
| `gr.Dropdown()` | Single or multi-select list. Set `multiselect=True` for multiple. |
| `gr.CheckboxGroup()` | Multiple selection from a predefined list. |
| `gr.Radio()` | Force single selection. |
| `gr.Checkbox()` | Boolean toggle. |
| `gr.File()` | File upload. Returns file path(s) to the backend function. |
| `gr.Image()` | Image upload. `type="pil"` returns a PIL Image object. |
| `gr.Label()` | Classification output. `num_top_classes=3` limits displayed classes. |

For LLM applications the output is almost always `gr.Textbox()` or just `"text"`.

