## Bugs Hit & Fixed

| Bug | Cause | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| `source: not recognized` | Lab uses bash syntax, running in PowerShell | Use `my_env\Scripts\Activate.ps1` to activate venv |
| `ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'gradio'` | Venv not activated | Activate venv first, then run script |
| `pydantic` build failure requiring Rust | Lab pins `pydantic==2.10.6`, no pre-built wheel for Python 3.11 on Windows | Drop pydantic pin, let it resolve as a dependency |
| `cannot import name 'HfFolder'` | Removed in newer `huggingface_hub` versions, unused in lab code | Delete the import |
| `TypeError: BlockContext.__init__() got an unexpected keyword argument 'allow_flagging'` | `allow_flagging` renamed in newer Gradio | Replace with `flagging_mode="never"` |
| Variable shadowing in `generate_response()` | Local variable named same as the function | Renamed local variable to `response` |

